\begin_layout Section
Forward contracts
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
forward contracts are traded over-the-counter(OTC) ——> standardized exchange-tra
ded contracts, such as those on the Chicago Mercantile Exchange, are known
 as 
\begin_inset Formula $futures$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Notation：
\begin_inset Formula $f_{t,T}$
\end_inset

 be the present value of a forward contract at time t maturing at time T;
 
\begin_inset Formula $F_{t,T}$
\end_inset

 be the forward price at time t, and 
\begin_inset Formula $r$
\end_inset

 be the risk-free rate per annum (with continuous compounding)
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
the forward price is such a delivery price K that makes the present value
 of a forward contract equal to zero, 
\begin_inset Formula $f_{0,T}=0$
\end_inset

:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
K=F_{0,T}=S_{0}e^{r(T-t_{0})}\tag{1.3}
\]

\end_inset

也就是说，the forward price理应按照无风险利率增长（否则就会有套利机会）
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
PV of a
\color red
 seasoned forward position at some 
\begin_inset Formula $t$
\end_inset

 after inception
\color inherit
, known as marking to market.
 At some time 
\begin_inset Formula $t$
\end_inset

 after inception, 
\begin_inset Formula $0<t<T$
\end_inset

, the PV is generally different from zero:
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
f_{t,T} & =e^{-r(T-t)}E_{t}[S_{T}-K]=S_{t}-e^{-r(T-t)}K=S_{t}-e^{r(T-t_{0})}S_{0}\\
 & =S_{t}-F_{0,t}=e^{-r(T-t)}[F_{t,T}-F_{0,T}]\tag{1.6}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

(远期的PV与当期远期价格和期初远期价格之差之间存在正向关系) Thus the PV of a seasoned forward contract
 can be valued by taking the difference between the forward price at time
 
\begin_inset Formula $t$
\end_inset

 and tht forward price at time 
\begin_inset Formula $0$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
it is important to note that the arbitrage-free and risk-neutral arguments
 are valid only for traded assets.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Value a forward on an asset providing a known cash income such as coupon
 bonds or stocks with discrete dividend payments.
 
\begin_inset Formula $I_{0}$
\end_inset

: the PV at time 
\begin_inset Formula $t_{0}$
\end_inset

of all income to be received from the asset between times 
\begin_inset Formula $t_{0}$
\end_inset

and 
\begin_inset Formula $T$
\end_inset

 (discounting at the risk-free rate), then
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
K=F_{0,T}=e^{r(T-t_{0})}(S_{0}-I_{0})
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
f_{t,T}=e^{-r(T-t)}E_{t}[(S_{T}-I_{T})-K]=S_{t}-I_{t}-e^{-r(T-t)}K
\]

\end_inset

if the asset pays a continuous known dividend yield 
\begin_inset Formula $q$
\end_inset

, then the frowth and discount rates are 
\begin_inset Formula $e^{(r-q)(T-t)}$
\end_inset

and 
\begin_inset Formula $e^{-(r-q)(T-t)}$
\end_inset

, respectively ; if the underlying asset is a foreign currency, then we
 can view the yield 
\begin_inset Formula $q$
\end_inset

 as the foreign risk-free rate 
\begin_inset Formula $r_{f}$
\end_inset

 so that the growth and discount rates of the underlying currency 
\begin_inset Formula $S_{0}$
\end_inset

are 
\begin_inset Formula $e^{(r-r_{f})(T-t)}$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $e^{-(r-r_{f})(T-t)}$
\end_inset

 , respectively , and the price of a forward contract on 
\begin_inset Formula $S_{0}$
\end_inset

at time 0 is 
\begin_inset Formula $F_{0,T}=S_{0}e^{(r-r_{f})(T-t)}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Section
Black-Scholes partial differential equaiton
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
假定
\begin_inset Formula $S_{t}$
\end_inset

为t时期一个risky stock that pays no dividends的价格，考虑其过程要满足三个限制条件：
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
价格永远非负（rules out arithmetic Brownian motion）
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
当价格为0时，企业破产，此时价格永远不会再为正，so zero should be an 
\begin_inset Formula $absorbing$
\end_inset

(cemetery) boundary。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
投资者要求的期望回报率应该独立于股票价格。
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
we choose the stochastic model 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
dS_{t}=mS_{t}dt+b(S_{t},t)dz_{t}\tag{1.10}
\]

\end_inset

其中，
\begin_inset Formula $m$
\end_inset

是drift coefficient（此情况下表示constant股票期望回报率），
\begin_inset Formula $b(S_{t},t)$
\end_inset

是diffusion coefficient，
\begin_inset Formula $z_{t}$
\end_inset

是Wiener process。当
\begin_inset Formula $b(S_{t},t)\equiv0$
\end_inset

，他表示一个risk-free asset。由于限制条件2，有
\begin_inset Formula $b(0,t)=0$
\end_inset

。thus we can 
\color red
parameterize
\color inherit
 our diffusion coefficient as follows:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
b(S,t)=\sigma(S,t)S\tag{1.11}
\]

\end_inset

其中，
\begin_inset Formula $\sigma(S,t)$
\end_inset

是一个关于
\begin_inset Formula $S$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $t$
\end_inset

的positive function，或者其他某个影响股票的随机变量，这里主要指股票价格的volatility。为便于分析，将其简化为一个常数
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
dS_{t}=mS_{t}dt+\sigma S_{t}dz_{t}\tag{1.12}
\]

\end_inset

the process is called 
\begin_inset Formula $geometric\,Brownian\,motions$
\end_inset

(geometric refers to the multiplicative nature of fluctuations)
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
引入一个变量：
\begin_inset Formula $x=f(S)=ln(S)$
\end_inset

，于是，依据Ito‘s lemma，任何一个关于S和t的函数满足：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
df=(\frac{\partial f}{\partial t}+mS\frac{\partial f}{\partial S}+\frac{1}{2}\sigma^{2}S^{2}\frac{\partial^{2}f}{\partial S^{2}})dt+\sigma S\frac{\partial f}{\partial S}dz\tag{1.14}
\]

\end_inset

将
\begin_inset Formula $x=f(S)=ln(S)$
\end_inset

’带入可得：
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
dx & =\mu dt+\sigma dz\\
 & =(m-\frac{\sigma^{2}}{2})dt+\sigma dz\tag{1.15}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

因此，股票价格的对数follows一个算术布朗运动，其drift rate是
\begin_inset Formula $\mu=m-\frac{\sigma^{2}}{2}$
\end_inset

且diffusion coefficient是
\begin_inset Formula $\sigma$
\end_inset

。【利用股票对数差的平均值计算出的是
\begin_inset Formula $m-\frac{\sigma^{2}}{2}$
\end_inset

吗？】对上式进行积分可得
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
x_{T}=x_{t}+(m-\frac{\sigma^{2}}{2})\tau+\sigma\sqrt{\tau}\varepsilon_{T}\tag{1.16}
\]

\end_inset

其中，
\begin_inset Formula $dz=\varepsilon\sqrt{dt}$
\end_inset

，
\begin_inset Formula $\tau=T-t$
\end_inset

，
\begin_inset Formula $\varepsilon$
\end_inset

是一个标准正态随机变量。进一步可得
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
ln\frac{S_{T}}{S_{t}}=(m-\frac{\sigma^{2}}{2})\tau+\sigma\sqrt{\tau}\varepsilon_{T}
\]

\end_inset

或者
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
S_{T}=S_{t}e^{(m-\frac{\sigma^{2}}{2})\tau+\sigma\sqrt{\tau}\varepsilon_{T}}
\]

\end_inset

this is the closed-form solution to the Brownian motion SDE。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
the transition probability density(the probability distribution function
 of 
\begin_inset Formula $S_{T}$
\end_inset

 at T given S at t)。Given x at t， 
\begin_inset Formula $x_{T}$
\end_inset

 is normally distributed:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
x_{T}\sim N(x_{t}+(m-\frac{\sigma^{2}}{2})(T-t),\sigma\sqrt{T-t})
\]

\end_inset

或者
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
p(x_{T},T|x_{t},t)dx_{T}=\frac{1}{\sqrt{2\pi\sigma^{2}(T-t)}}e^{-\frac{(x_{T}-x_{t}-\mu(T-t))^{2}}{2\sigma^{2}(T-t)}}dx_{T}\tag{1.20}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Calculate the moments of the lognormal distribution around zero
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
M_{n}(0)=E_{t,S}[S_{T}^{n}]=\int_{0}^{\infty}S_{T}^{n}p(S_{T},T|S_{t},t)dS_{T}\tag{1.22}
\]

\end_inset

注意积分区间从0开始，因为股价非负。由于
\begin_inset Formula $S_{T}=e^{x_{T}}$
\end_inset

，于是，我们需要计算
\begin_inset Formula $M_{n}(0)=E_{t,x}[e^{nx_{T}}]$
\end_inset

，可以利用正态分布的特征方程：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\phi(\lambda)=E[e^{i\lambda x_{T}}]=exp[i\lambda(x+\mu\tau)-\frac{\sigma^{2}\tau\lambda^{2}}{2}]\tag{1.24}
\]

\end_inset

将
\begin_inset Formula $i\lambda$
\end_inset

换成
\begin_inset Formula $n$
\end_inset

，于是
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
M_{n}(0) & =E_{t,S}[e^{nx_{T}}]=S^{n}exp[n\mu\tau+\frac{n^{2}\sigma^{2}\tau}{2}]\tag{1.25}\\
 & =S^{n}exp[nm\tau+\frac{n(n-1)}{2}\sigma^{2}\tau]\tag{1.26}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

当n=1时，可以得到
\begin_inset Formula $S_{T}$
\end_inset

的期望为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
E_{t,S}[S_{T}]=e^{m\tau}S\tag{1.27}
\]

\end_inset

方差为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
Var_{t,S}=E_{t,S}[S_{T}^{2}]-[E_{t,S}(S_{T})]^{2}=S^{2}[e^{2m\tau+\sigma^{2}\tau}-e^{2m\tau}]=S^{2}e^{2m\tau}[e^{\sigma^{2}\tau}-1]
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
推导股票衍生品价格。假定衍生证券
\begin_inset Formula $f_{T}=F(S_{T})$
\end_inset

，且标的资产价格服从几何布朗运动（如式(1.12)描述）。构建一个投资组合
\begin_inset Formula $\Pi$
\end_inset

：short position in one derivative security 
\begin_inset Formula $f$
\end_inset

 and long position in a certain number of shares 
\begin_inset Formula $\Delta$
\end_inset

，于是
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\Pi=\Delta S-f\tag{1.28}
\]

\end_inset

于是，由Ito‘s lemma，在一个足够小的时间区间
\begin_inset Formula $dt$
\end_inset

内，
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
d\Pi & =\Delta dS-df\\
 & =\Delta(mSdt+\sigma Sdz)-(\frac{\partial f}{\partial t}+mS\frac{\partial f}{\partial S}+\frac{1}{2}\sigma^{2}S^{2}\frac{\partial^{2}f}{\partial S^{2}})dt-\sigma S\frac{\partial f}{\partial S}dz\\
 & =\sigma S(\Delta-\frac{\partial f}{\partial S})dz+[mS(\Delta-\frac{\partial f}{\partial S})-\frac{\partial f}{\partial t}-\frac{1}{2}\sigma^{2}S^{2}\frac{\partial^{2}f}{\partial S^{2}}]dt\tag{1.31}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

当我们选取
\begin_inset Formula $\Delta=\frac{\partial f}{\partial S}$
\end_inset

(the hedge ratio)，发现组合变成了无风险资产组合，于是
\begin_inset Formula $d\Pi=r\Pi dt$
\end_inset

，结合式(1.31)有
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{\partial f}{\partial t}+\frac{1}{2}\sigma^{2}S^{2}\frac{\partial^{2}f}{\partial S^{2}}+r\Pi=0\tag{1.34}
\]

\end_inset

或者
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{1}{2}\sigma^{2}S^{2}\frac{\partial^{2}f}{\partial S^{2}}+r(\frac{\partial f}{\partial S}S-f)=\frac{1}{2}\sigma^{2}S^{2}\frac{\partial^{2}f}{\partial S^{2}}+rS\frac{\partial f}{\partial S}-rf=-\frac{\partial f}{\partial t}\tag{1.35}
\]

\end_inset

于是衍生证券
\begin_inset Formula $f$
\end_inset

满足partial differential equations(PDEs) as a consequence of the no-arbitrage
 assumption。这就是Black-Scholes equation，mathematically， this is a diffusion
 or heat equation。
\end_layout

