\color red
一个疑问
\color inherit
：似乎欧式期权的边界值S-K或者K-S并不满足BS PDE
\end_layout

\begin_layout Section
Risk-neutral pricing
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
在风险中性世界分析式(1.35)，将其重写为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
D_{s,t}f-rf=-\frac{\partial f}{\partial t}\tag{1.36}
\]

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
D_{s,t}=\frac{1}{2}\sigma^{2}S^{2}\frac{\partial^{2}}{\partial S^{2}}+rS\frac{\partial}{\partial S}\tag{1.37}
\]

\end_inset

注意真实世界中的drift rate 
\begin_inset Formula $m$
\end_inset

并没有出现在上述方程中；从上述方程可以看出，在风险中性世界中，drift rate是risk-free rate 
\begin_inset Formula $r$
\end_inset

，于是在风险中性世界中，价格过程满足
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
dS=rSdt+\sigma Sdz\tag{1.38}
\]

\end_inset

注意到delta(the hedge ratio) 依赖于具体的时间和标的价格：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\Delta(S,t)=\frac{\partial f(S,t)}{\partial S}\tag{1.39}
\]

\end_inset

因此，需要动态对冲策略，否则，前述复制的资产组合不再是无风险资产。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
假定世界只存在三种不同的资产：股票，欧式齐全以及货币基金(one share priced at 
\begin_inset Formula $A_{0}=1$
\end_inset

 at time 0)。据此构建资产组合：sell one option(short) for 
\begin_inset Formula $f_{0}$
\end_inset

；buy 
\begin_inset Formula $\Delta_{0}$
\end_inset

 shares of stock：sell(short) 
\begin_inset Formula $N_{0}$
\end_inset

shares of the money market account(this is equivalent to borrowing 
\begin_inset Formula $N_{0}$
\end_inset

dollars at the risk-free money market rate 
\begin_inset Formula $r$
\end_inset

)，于是资产组合在期初的价值Wiener：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\Pi_{0}=\Delta_{0}S_{0}-N_{0}-f_{0}\tag{1.40}
\]

\end_inset

持有过程中，不断调整
\begin_inset Formula $\Delta$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $N$
\end_inset

。在某个时间t，资产组合价值为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\Pi_{t}=\Delta_{t}S_{t}-N_{t}A_{t}-f_{t}\tag{1.41}
\]

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula $A_{t}=e^{rt}$
\end_inset

。 A pair of stochastic processes {(
\begin_inset Formula $\Delta t$
\end_inset

,
\begin_inset Formula $N_{t}$
\end_inset

),
\begin_inset Formula $0\leq t\leq T$
\end_inset

} that is a sequence of trading decisions is a 
\begin_inset Formula $dynamic\,trading\,strategy$
\end_inset

 ：the 
\begin_inset Formula $\Delta_{t}$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $N_{t}$
\end_inset

, viewed as functions of time, are stochastic processes since we do not
 know their values at the beginning of our future trading decisions
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\Delta_{t}=\Delta(S_{t},t)
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
N_{t}=N(S_{t},t)
\]

\end_inset

在一段足够小的时间
\begin_inset Formula $dt$
\end_inset

后，组合变化为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
d\Pi_{t}=\Delta_{t}dS_{t}-N_{t}dA_{t}-df_{t}+d\Delta_{t}(S_{t}+dS_{t})-dN_{t}(A_{t}+dA_{t})\tag{1.42}
\]

\end_inset

源于
\begin_inset Formula $\Pi_{t}+d\Pi_{t}=(\Delta_{t}+d\Delta_{t})(S_{t}+dS_{t})-(N_{t}+dN_{t})(A_{t}+dA_{t})-(f_{t}+df_{t})$
\end_inset

。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
定义：a dynamic trading strategy 
\begin_inset Formula $\phi\equiv\{(\Delta_{t},N_{t}),0\leq t\leq T\}$
\end_inset

 is said to be 
\begin_inset Formula $self-financing$
\end_inset

 if no capital is added to or withdrawn from the portfolio 
\begin_inset Formula $\Pi_{t}$
\end_inset

 after the initial setup at time 0。式(1.42)中， 
\begin_inset Formula $self-financing$
\end_inset

发生，当且仅当
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
d\Delta_{t}(S_{t}+dS_{t})-dN_{t}(A_{t}+dA_{t})=0\tag{1.45}
\]

\end_inset

此方程被称为
\begin_inset Formula $balance\,equation$
\end_inset

，事实上，
\begin_inset Formula $d\Delta_{t}(S_{t}+dS_{t})$
\end_inset

表示投入到股票中的总资金的变化【注意是总资金变化，而不是总价值变化，二者是有区别的】，
\begin_inset Formula $dN_{t}(A_{t}+dA_{t})$
\end_inset

是债务变化(同样是货币上的变化)。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
上述交易策略总的收益可以看成是每个小区间
\begin_inset Formula $dt$
\end_inset

的总和
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\Pi_{T}-\Pi_{0} & =\underset{\Delta t\rightarrow0}{lim}[\Sigma_{t=0}^{N-1}\Delta(S_{i},t_{i})(S_{i+1}-S_{i})-\Sigma_{i=0}^{N-1}N(S_{i},t_{i})(A(t_{i+1})-A(t_{i}))]-[f(S_{T},T)-f(S_{0},0)]\tag{1.46}\\
 & =\int_{0}^{T}\Delta_{t}dS_{t}-\int_{0}^{T}N_{t}dA_{t}-[F(S_{T})-f(S_{0},0)]\tag{1.47}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula $F(S_{T})$
\end_inset

是payoff from the derivative，
\begin_inset Formula $\int_{0}^{T}\Delta_{t}dS_{t}$
\end_inset

需要用到Ito integral（见Appendix B）
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
如果存在一个self-financing策略能够完全复制出the option with the given payoff 
\begin_inset Formula $F(S_{T})$
\end_inset

，那么根据无套利原则，对于任何时点t，有
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\Delta_{t}S_{t}-N_{t}A_{t}-f_{t}=0\tag{1.48}
\]

\end_inset

根据Ito‘s lemma ，可以用一个过程描述期权价格：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
df=m_{f}fdt+\sigma_{f}fdz\tag{1.49}
\]

\end_inset

由式(1.14)可知
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
m_{f}=\frac{\frac{\partial f}{\partial t}+mS\frac{\partial f}{\partial S}+\frac{1}{2}\sigma^{2}S^{2}\frac{\partial^{2}f}{\partial S^{2}}}{f}\tag{1.50}
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\sigma_{f}=\frac{\sigma S\frac{\partial f}{\partial S}}{f}\tag{1.51}
\]

\end_inset

由式(1.48)，在足够小的时间区间
\begin_inset Formula $dt$
\end_inset

内
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\Delta_{t}dS_{t}-N_{t}dA_{t}-df_{t}=0
\]

\end_inset

或者
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\Delta(mSdt+\sigma Sdz)-NrAdt-(m_{f}fdt+\sigma_{f}fdz)=0\tag{1.52}
\]

\end_inset

又
\begin_inset Formula $NA=\Delta S-f$
\end_inset

，带入上式，得
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
[(m_{f}-r)f-\Delta S(m-r)]dt+(\sigma_{f}f-\Delta\sigma S)dz=0\tag{1.53}
\]

\end_inset

显然，由于
\begin_inset Formula $dz$
\end_inset

的存在，上式不恒等于0，除非
\begin_inset Formula $(\sigma_{f}f-\Delta\sigma S=0$
\end_inset

，于是
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\Delta=\frac{\sigma_{f}f}{\sigma S}=\frac{\partial f}{\partial S}\tag{1.54}
\]

\end_inset

进一步，有
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
m_{f}=r+\frac{\sigma_{f}}{\sigma}(m-r)
\]

\end_inset

或者
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{m_{f}-r}{\sigma_{f}}=\frac{m-r}{\sigma}\equiv\lambda\tag{1.55}
\]

\end_inset

式(1.54)说明delta（the hedge ratio）也是actual price volatility of the option to
 the actual price volatility of the stock；式(1.55) is the central relation
 of the arbitrage pricing theory，and is known as the 
\begin_inset Formula $market\,price\,of\,risk$
\end_inset

 and is fundamental to general derivatives pricing since it is used to change
 probability measures in one stochastic process to an equivalent martingale
 measure in another process according to 
\begin_inset Formula $Girsanov's\,theorem$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
