\begin_inset Formula $m_{f}$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $\sigma_{f}$
\end_inset

的表达式带入(1.55)可得
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{\partial f}{\partial t}+mS\frac{\partial f}{\partial S}+\frac{1}{2}\sigma^{2}S^{2}\frac{\partial^{2}f}{\partial S^{2}}=rf+(m-r)S\frac{\partial f}{\partial S}
\]

\end_inset

也就是
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{\partial f}{\partial t}+rS\frac{\partial f}{\partial S}+\frac{1}{2}\sigma^{2}S^{2}\frac{\partial^{2}f}{\partial S^{2}}=rf\tag{1.56}
\]

\end_inset

这意味着：（1）为避免套利机会的存在，期权价格一定满足BS PDE；（2）动态复制策略是唯一的
