\begin_layout Chapter
Binomial trees
\end_layout

\begin_layout Section
use of binomial trees
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
一个简单的单期二叉树：在风险中性世界中，有
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
pSu+(1-p)Sd=Se^{r\Delta t}\tag{3.1}
\]

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula $p=\frac{e^{r\Delta r}-d}{u-d}$
\end_inset

。对于u和d，常见的设置是
\begin_inset Formula $u=1/d=e^{\sigma\Delta t}$
\end_inset

（非必要）
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
拓展为多期：假定将到期时间T均等划分为N段（最后的时间点上有N+1个节点 ，整个二叉树共有
\begin_inset Formula $2^{N}$
\end_inset

中路径），在节点
\begin_inset Formula $(i,j)$
\end_inset

上有
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
S_{i,j}=S_{0}u^{i}d^{i-j}\quad i=0,1,...,N;\quad j=0,1,...,i\tag{3.2}
\]

\end_inset

到期时间点上的payoff为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
f_{N,j}=F(S_{0}u^{j}d^{N-j})\tag{3.3}
\]

\end_inset

可以通过backward induction的方法推导欧式期权价格：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
f=e^{-rT}\Sigma_{j=1}^{N}p_{N,j}f_{N,j}\tag{3.5}
\]

\end_inset

其中，
\begin_inset Formula $p_{N,j}=C_{N}^{j}p^{j}(1-p)^{N-j}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
离散时间的多期二叉树模型收敛到连续时间的Black-Scholes-Merton模型，即当
\begin_inset Formula $N\rightarrow\infty,\Delta t\rightarrow0$
\end_inset

，有
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
f\rightarrow e^{-rT}\int_{0}^{\infty}F(S_{T})p^{Q}(S_{T},T|S,t)dS_{T}\tag{3.7}
\]

\end_inset

这要求the distribution of the terminal stock price in the binomial model converge
 to the lognormal distribution as 
\begin_inset Formula $\Delta t\rightarrow0$
\end_inset

。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Proposition：the distribution of the terminal stock price in the binomial
 model with parameters 
\begin_inset Formula $(u,d,p,r)$
\end_inset

 converges to the Black-Scholes lognormal distribution with parameters 
\begin_inset Formula $(\sigma,r)$
\end_inset

 as 
\begin_inset Formula $\Delta t\rightarrow0$
\end_inset

 if and only if：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
pln(\frac{u}{d})+lnd=\mu\Delta t+o(\Delta t)\tag{3.8}
\]

\end_inset

and
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
p(1-p)[ln(\frac{u}{d})]^{2}=\sigma^{2}\Delta t+o(\Delta t)\tag{3.9}
\]

\end_inset

Proof：In the Black-Scholes model, the terminal stock price is a random variable：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
S_{T}=S*e^{\mu T+\sigma\sqrt{T}\varepsilon_{T}}
\]

\end_inset

the continuously compounded return over the time period 
\begin_inset Formula $T$
\end_inset

 is a normal random variable：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\eta=ln(\frac{S_{T}}{S})=\mu T+\sigma\sqrt{T}\varepsilon_{T}\tag{3.10}
\]

\end_inset

where 
\begin_inset Formula $\mu=m-\frac{\sigma^{2}}{2}$
\end_inset

。在二叉树模型中，将时间区间划分为N份，股票总的return（log-return）为
\begin_inset Formula $\eta=\Sigma_{i=1}^{N}\eta_{i}$
\end_inset

，其中
\begin_inset Formula $\eta_{i}$
\end_inset

是在第i个小区间上的return，它是
\begin_inset Formula $i.i.d$
\end_inset

的随机变量：以概率
\begin_inset Formula $p$
\end_inset

取值ln
\begin_inset Formula $u$
\end_inset

，以概率
\begin_inset Formula $(1-p)$
\end_inset

取值ln
\begin_inset Formula $d$
\end_inset

，其均值和方差分别为：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
m=plnu+(1-p)lnd
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
s^{2} & =p(lnu)^{2}+(1-p)(lnd)^{2}-(plnu+(1-p)lnd)^{2}\\
 & =p(1-p)[ln(\frac{u}{d})]
\end{align*}

\end_inset

由中心极限定理可得，若二叉树模型最终收敛到BS模型当且仅当：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\Sigma_{i=1}^{N}\eta_{i}\rightarrow\mu T+\sigma\sqrt{T}\varepsilon_{T}\quad(N\rightarrow\infty\text{或}\Delta t\rightarrow0)
\]

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
mN\rightarrow\mu T=\mu\Delta tN
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
s^{2}N\rightarrow\sigma^{2}T=\sigma^{2}\Delta tN
\]

\end_inset

即
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
m=pln(\frac{u}{d})+lnd=\mu\Delta t+o(\Delta t)
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
s^{2}=p(1-p)[ln(\frac{u}{d})]^{2}=\sigma^{2}\Delta t+o(\Delta t)
\]

\end_inset

得证。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
更一般的证明：首先，根据二叉树模型：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
C_{binomial}=R^{-n}\{\Sigma_{j=0}^{n}C_{n}^{j}p^{j}(1-p)^{n-j}*max[Su^{j}d^{n-j},0]\}\tag{3.13}
\]

\end_inset

令a表示当期权最终处于in-the-money状态时，二叉树中至少经历的上升的次数，即a是使得
\begin_inset Formula $Su^{a}d^{n-a}>X$
\end_inset

成立的最小非负整数，于是
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
a>\frac{log(\frac{X}{Sd^{n}})}{log(\frac{u}{d})}
\]

\end_inset

此时，对于所有
\begin_inset Formula $j\geq a$
\end_inset

，
\begin_inset Formula $max[Su^{j}d^{n-j}-X,0]=Su^{j}d^{n-j}-X$
\end_inset

，其他为0，因此
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
C_{binomial}=R^{-n}\{\Sigma_{j=a}^{n}C_{n}^{j}p^{j}(1-p)^{n-j}*Su^{j}d^{n-j}\}\tag{3.15}
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
C_{binomial}=S[\Sigma_{j=a}^{n}C_{n}^{j}p^{j}(1-p)^{n-j}(\frac{u^{j}d^{n-j}}{R^{n}})]-XR^{-n}[\Sigma_{j=a}^{n}C_{n}^{j}p^{j}(1-p)^{n-j}]\tag{3.16}
\]

\end_inset

令
\begin_inset Formula $p'\equiv(u/R)p$
\end_inset

，且
\begin_inset Formula $1-p'\equiv(d/R)(1-p)$
\end_inset

，于是
\begin_inset Formula $p^{j}(1-p)^{n-j}(\frac{u^{j}d^{n-j}}{R^{n}})=p'^{j}(1-p')^{n-j}$
\end_inset

。因此，式(3.16)可以写成
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
C_{binomial} & =S[\Sigma_{j=a}^{n}C_{n}^{j}p'^{j}(1-p')^{n-j}]-XR^{-n}[\Sigma_{j=a}^{n}C_{n}^{j}p^{j}(1-p)^{n-j}]\\
 & S\Phi[a;n,p']-XR^{-n}\Phi[a;n,p]\tag{3.19}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

下面就需要证明：
\begin_inset Formula $\Phi[a;n,p']\rightarrow N(d),\Phi[a;n,p]\rightarrow N(d-\sigma\sqrt{T})$
\end_inset

【证明会利用到式(3.8-9)，暂略】
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
为加速二叉树模型收敛到BS模型，可以通过让单期二叉树的均值和方差与对数正态的均值、方差相匹配，具体：首先，
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
S_{t+\Delta t}=S_{t}exp(\mu\Delta t+\sigma\sqrt{\Delta t})
\]

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula $\mu=r-\sigma^{2}/2$
\end_inset

，于是，其期望和方差为：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
E_{t,S}^{Q}[S_{t+\Delta t}]=e^{r\Delta t}S_{t}\tag{3.27}
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
Var_{t,S}^{Q}[S_{t+\Delta t}]=e^{2r\Delta t}(e^{\sigma^{2}\Delta t}-1)S_{t}^{2}\tag{3.28}
\]

\end_inset

其中，Q表示风险中性测度。又单期二叉树模型的均值和二阶原点矩为：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
E_{t,S}^{binomial}[S_{t+\Delta t}]=[pu+(1-p)d]S_{t}\tag{3.29}
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
E_{t,S}^{binomial}[S_{t+\Delta t}^{2}]=[pu^{2}+(1-p)d^{2}]S_{t}^{2}\tag{3.30}
\]

\end_inset

于是，令
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
pu+(1-p)d=e^{r\Delta t}\tag{3.31}
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
pu^{2}+(1-p)d^{2}=e^{(2r+\sigma^{2})\Delta t}3.32
\]

\end_inset

这是只有两个等式的三元方程组。对其进行简单的整理，有：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
p=\frac{e^{r\Delta t}-d}{u-d}
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
e^{r\Delta t}(u+d)-du=e^{(2r+\sigma^{2})\Delta t}\tag{3.33}
\]

\end_inset

为了解出p，u以及d，需要额外的方程，于是就有三种常见的方法：（1）Cox-Ross-Rubinstein；（2）Jarrow-Rudd；（3）a
 general approach。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Section
Cox-Ross-Rubinstein binomial tree
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
CRR假定一个关系式
\begin_inset Formula $du=1$
\end_inset

，于是，式(3.33)可以改写为
\begin_inset Formula $d^{2}-2Ad+1=0$
\end_inset

，
\begin_inset Formula $A=(e^{-r\Delta t}+e^{(r+\sigma^{2})\Delta t})/2$
\end_inset

，于是，可以解得：
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
u & =A+\sqrt{A^{2}-1}\tag{3.34}\\
d & =A-\sqrt{A^{2}-1}\tag{3.35}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

对其进行线性化处理(省略
\begin_inset Formula $\Delta t$
\end_inset

的高阶项)，可以得到：
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
u & =1+\sigma\sqrt{\Delta t}+\frac{1}{2}\sigma^{2}\Delta t\\
d & =1-\sigma\sqrt{\Delta t}+\frac{1}{2}\sigma^{2}\Delta t\\
p & =\frac{1}{2}+\frac{1}{2}\frac{\mu}{\sigma}\sqrt{\Delta t}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

实际上，更常用的形式是
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
u & =e^{\sigma\sqrt{\Delta t}}\\
d & =e^{-\sigma\sqrt{\Delta t}}\\
p & =\frac{e^{r\Delta t}-d}{u-d}
\end{align*}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Section
Jarrow-Rubb binomial tree
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
JR将p值固定为0.5，于是，式(3.31-2)变为
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
u+d & =2e^{r\Delta t}\tag{3.36}\\
u^{2}+d^{2} & =2e^{(2r+\sigma^{2})\Delta t}\tag{3.37}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

其解为
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
u & =e^{r\Delta t}(1+\sqrt{e^{\sigma^{2}\Delta t}-1})\tag{3.38}\\
d & =e^{r\Delta t}(1-\sqrt{e^{\sigma^{2}\Delta t}-1})\tag{3.39}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

同样地，一个线性近似解为
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
u & =1+r\Delta t+\sigma\sqrt{\Delta t}\\
d & =1-r\Delta t+\sigma\sqrt{\Delta t}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

实际上，对于JR binomial tree，更常见的选择是：
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
u & =e^{\mu\Delta t+\sigma\sqrt{\Delta t}}\tag{3.40}\\
d & =e^{\mu\Delta t-\sigma\sqrt{\Delta t}}\tag{3.41}\\
p & =0.5
\end{align*}

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula $\mu=r-\sigma^{2}/2$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Section
General tree
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
假定
\begin_inset Formula $ud=e^{2v\Delta t}$
\end_inset

，其中
\begin_inset Formula $v$
\end_inset

是一个标量，于是：
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
u & =e^{v\Delta t+\sigma\sqrt{\Delta t}}\tag{3.42}\\
d & =e^{v\Delta t-\sigma\sqrt{\Delta t}}\tag{3.42}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

此时，相应的p值约为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
p=\frac{1}{2}+\frac{1}{2}(\frac{\mu-v}{\sigma})\sqrt{\Delta t}
\]

\end_inset

实际上，CRR和JR相应的v值分别为
\begin_inset Formula $v=0$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $v=\mu$
\end_inset

。但是，请注意：CRR和JR仅对较小的时间区间上有一个比较好的近似。对此，一个比较好的解决方法是reformulating the problem
 in terms of the natural logarithm of the asset price：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
dx=\mu dt+\sigma dz
\]

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula $x=lnS$
\end_inset

，
\begin_inset Formula $\mu=r-\sigma^{2}/2$
\end_inset

。于是
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
E[\Delta x] & =p_{u}\Delta x_{u}+p_{d}\Delta x_{d}=\mu\Delta t\\
E[\Delta x^{2}] & =p_{u}\Delta x_{u}^{2}+p_{d}\Delta x_{d}^{2}=\sigma^{2}\Delta t+\mu^{2}\Delta t^{2}\tag{3.44}
\end{align*}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
方法一：令
\begin_inset Formula $p_{d}=p_{u}$
\end_inset

，则
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
(\Delta x_{u}+\Delta x_{d})/2 & =\mu\Delta t\\
(\Delta x_{u}^{2}+\Delta x_{d}^{2})/2 & =\sigma^{2}\Delta t+\mu^{2}\Delta t^{2}\tag{3.45}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

解得
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\Delta x_{u} & =\frac{1}{2}\mu\Delta t+\frac{1}{2}\sqrt{4\sigma^{2}\Delta t-3\mu^{2}\Delta t^{2}}\\
\Delta x_{d} & =\frac{1}{2}\mu\Delta t-\frac{1}{2}\sqrt{4\sigma^{2}\Delta t-3\mu^{2}\Delta t^{2}}\tag{3.46}
\end{align*}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
方法二：令
\begin_inset Formula $\Delta x_{u}=\Delta x_{d}$
\end_inset

，同理，可解得
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\Delta x & =\sqrt{\sigma^{2}\Delta t+\mu^{2}\Delta t^{2}}\\
p_{u} & =\frac{1}{2}+\frac{1}{2}\frac{\mu\Delta t}{\Delta x}\tag{3.48}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

此方法是由Trigeorgis(1991)提出，一般来说，在精度上，此方法稍好于CRR和JR模型
\end_layout

