\begin_layout Section
Jarrow-Rubb trinomial tree
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
在Monte-Carlo计算过程中，我们采用下式进行股票路径的模拟：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
S_{i+1}=S_{i}e^{\mu\Delta t+\sigma\sqrt{\Delta t}\varepsilon_{i+1}}
\]

\end_inset

我们希望利用三叉树去逼近最终的(对数)正态分布。于是，我们需要匹配两个分布的均值和方差。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
首先，JR三叉树的结构：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
S_{i+1}=\begin{cases}
S_{i}U=S_{i}e^{\mu\Delta t+\lambda\sigma\sqrt{\Delta t}}\\
S_{i}M=S_{i}e^{\mu\Delta t} & \tag{4.3}\\
S_{i}D=S_{i}e^{\mu\Delta t-\lambda\sigma\sqrt{\Delta t}}
\end{cases}
\]

\end_inset

相应的概率分别为
\begin_inset Formula $p_{u},p_{m},p_{d}$
\end_inset

，显然满足
\begin_inset Formula $p_{u}+p_{m}+p_{d}=1$
\end_inset

。（注意：The necessary and sufficient condition for the tree to recombine is
 : 
\begin_inset Formula $UD=M^{2}$
\end_inset

。简单地说就是保证节点重合，使得节点数线性增长）。记
\begin_inset Formula $U=ue^{\mu\Delta t},D=de^{\mu\Delta t},k=e^{\sigma^{2}\Delta t/2}$
\end_inset

。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
均值方差匹配。首先，均值匹配要求：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
E_{t,S}^{trinomial}[S_{t+\Delta t}]=E_{t,S}^{Q}[S_{t+\Delta t}]=Se^{r\Delta t}
\]

\end_inset

即
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
p_{u}u+p_{m}+p_{d}d=k\tag{4.4}
\]

\end_inset

二阶矩匹配（等价于方差匹配）要求：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
E_{t,S}^{trinomial}[S_{t+\Delta t}^{2}]=E_{t,S}^{Q}[S_{t+\Delta t}^{2}]=S^{2}e^{(2r+\sigma^{2})\Delta t}
\]

\end_inset

即
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
p_{u}u^{2}+p_{m}+p_{d}d^{2}=k^{5}\tag{4.5}
\]

\end_inset

可以解得
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
p_{u} & =\frac{k^{4}-(d+1)k+d}{(u-d)(u-1)}\tag{4.6}\\
p_{d} & =\frac{k^{4}-(u+1)k+u}{(u-d)(1-d)}\tag{4.7}\\
p_{m} & =1-p_{u}-p_{d}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula $u=e^{\lambda\sigma\sqrt{\Delta t}},d=e^{-\lambda\sigma\sqrt{\Delta t}},k=e^{\sigma^{2}\Delta t/2}$
\end_inset

【注意，只要
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda$
\end_inset

的选取使得所有概率取值为正，则结果都会收敛，只是收敛速度不同】
\end_layout

\begin_layout Section
Cox-Ross-Rubinstein trinomial tree
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
类似的，CRR三叉树的结构为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
S_{i+1}=\begin{cases}
S_{i}U=S_{i}e^{\lambda\sigma\sqrt{\Delta t}}\\
S_{i}M=S_{i} & \tag{}\\
S_{i}D=S_{i}e^{-\lambda\sigma\sqrt{\Delta t}}
\end{cases}
\]

\end_inset

即CRR三叉树令M=1。同样利用前两阶矩匹配可以得到：
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
p_{u} & =\frac{1}{2\lambda^{2}}+\frac{1}{2}(\frac{\mu}{\lambda\sigma})\sqrt{\Delta t}\tag{4.8}\\
p_{d} & =\frac{1}{2\lambda^{2}}-\frac{1}{2}(\frac{\mu}{\lambda\sigma})\sqrt{\Delta t}\tag{4.9}\\
p_{m} & =1-\frac{1}{\lambda^{2}}\tag{4.10}
\end{align*}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Section
Optimal choice of 
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Kamrad and Ritchken(1991) 建议取
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda=\sqrt{3/2}$
\end_inset

可以使得收敛速度最快。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
当
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda=\sqrt{3/2}$
\end_inset

时，CRR参数设定为：
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
