p_{d} & =\frac{1}{3}-(\frac{\mu}{\sigma})\sqrt{\frac{\Delta t}{6}}\\
p_{m} & =\frac{1}{3}\\
U & =e^{\sigma\sqrt{3\Delta t/2}}\\
M & =1\\
D & =e^{-\sigma\sqrt{3\Delta t/2}}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

【注意】对于CRR三叉树而言，当
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda=1$
\end_inset

时就变成了二叉树；
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda<1$
